<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <meta name="env" content="<%= process.env.NODE_ENV || 'production' %>">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/bootstrap-grid.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/global.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/documentations.css">
  <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/assets/ico/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon"/>
</head>
<body class="compact">

  <%- include('partials/navbar', { currentPage: 'documentations', user: user }) %>

  <div class="container-fluid main-content">
    <main class="content">
      <div class="docs-container-wrapper">
        <section class="card panels docs-card-container">
          <div class="docs-modern-container">
        
        <div class="docs-header">
          <div class="docs-header-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/>
              <path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h1 class="docs-title">Development Guide</h1>
          <p class="docs-subtitle">Complete documentation to develop with MicroCoaster, manage your ESP32 modules and create innovative interactive experiences.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="docs-cards-grid">
          
          <div class="docs-card">
            <div class="docs-card-icon getting-started">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <rect x="4" y="4" width="6" height="6"/>
                <rect x="14" y="4" width="6" height="6"/>
                <rect x="4" y="14" width="6" height="6"/>
                <rect x="14" y="14" width="6" height="6"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>ESP32 Configuration</h3>
            <p>Step-by-step guide to configure your ESP32 modules, connect your sensors and actuators to your MicroCoaster circuit.</p>
            <a href="#esp32-config" class="docs-card-link">
              Browse docs
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="m9 18 6-6-6-6"/>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="docs-card">
            <div class="docs-card-icon authentication">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
                <polyline points="12,6 12,12 16,14"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Timeline Sequencer</h3>
            <p>Create complex automated sequences to synchronize your effects: lights, sounds, smoke and movements.</p>
            <a href="#timeline" class="docs-card-link">
              Browse docs
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="m9 18 6-6-6-6"/>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="docs-card">
            <div class="docs-card-icon modules">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <polygon points="11 5 6 9 2 9 2 15 6 15 11 19 11 5"/>
                <path d="M19.07 4.93a10 10 0 0 1 0 14.14M15.54 8.46a5 5 0 0 1 0 7.07"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Module Types</h3>
            <p>Discover all available modules: Audio Player, Light FX, Smoke Machine, Station, Switch Track and Launch Track.</p>
            <a href="#modules" class="docs-card-link">
              Browse docs
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="m9 18 6-6-6-6"/>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="docs-card">
            <div class="docs-card-icon advanced">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Track Management</h3>
            <p>Learn how to organize your circuit, manage tracks, configure switches and optimize your train flow.</p>
            <a href="#circuit" class="docs-card-link">
              Browse docs
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="m9 18 6-6-6-6"/>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="docs-card">
            <div class="docs-card-icon api">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5"/>
                <line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="3"/>
                <line x1="12" y1="21" x2="12" y2="23"/>
                <line x1="4.22" y1="4.22" x2="5.64" y2="5.64"/>
                <line x1="18.36" y1="18.36" x2="19.78" y2="19.78"/>
                <line x1="1" y1="12" x2="3" y2="12"/>
                <line x1="21" y1="12" x2="23" y2="12"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Special Effects</h3>
            <p>Master lighting, sound and smoke effects to create immersive experiences in your miniature park.</p>
            <a href="#effects" class="docs-card-link">
              Browse docs
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="m9 18 6-6-6-6"/>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="docs-card">
            <div class="docs-card-icon enterprise">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/>
                <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Troubleshooting & Support</h3>
            <p>Solutions to common problems, offline module diagnostics, and tips to maintain your MicroCoaster installation.</p>
            <a href="#troubleshooting" class="docs-card-link">
              Browse docs
              <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="m9 18 6-6-6-6"/>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>

        </div>
      </section>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>

  <script src="/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/global.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/language.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
